text: Arest on þane reanden weg ðat on ðone forde to teofunte þanen.
On brochenenberge ðat on hoddes clif.
Þanen on abbenbeorg ðat on stortencumb on ðes linkes havede suthward.
And northward þanen on leon berg þat on ða ealden dich þanne.
Onne þat furch ðe is aðe riuen to nodre þannen on funtnesford þannen on herepaþ on þe reden wege on þa two meades oþer be nodre oþer be wilig ðe ðarto herað.
